author: andreasmyth
msg: Decoupled creation of endpoint from its publishing.
Publish only a selected endpoint instead of all as in systests2 GreeterTest.

For that purpose need information from implementor class not available through JaxwsServiceFactoryBean, or JaxwsServiceConfiguration. Created JaxwsImplementorInfo for that purpose and used it in JaxwsServiceFactoryBean to avoid duplication.
Removed overwrite of setServiceClass in JaxwsServiceFactoryBean (with fixes to JaxwsServiceConfiguration no longer needed).
Changed build order to build transports/local before frontend-jaxws - other transports later (alternative: make ClientTest a unit test and/or move to systests2).
